sources.title: White Zombie 1932 | Bela Lugosi, Madge Bellamy, Joseph Cawthorn | Horror Movie
sources.description:
With these zombie eyes he rendered her powerless - with this zombie grip he made her perform his every desire!
Set in Haiti,  young man turns to a witch doctor to lure Madeleine, the woman he loves, away from her fiancé, but instead turns her into a zombie slave. Her fiancé Neil struggles to save her, he must navigate through a world filled with dark rituals and undead minions to reclaim his beloved.

Original title: White Zombie (1932) 


Colorized version https://youtu.be/IErsYNaK_-w

Director: Victor Halperin 
Writers: Garnett Weston, Garnett Weston 
Stars: Bela Lugosi, Madge Bellamy, Joseph Cawthorn
Genre: Classics, Cult Film, Crime, Horror, Sci-Fi 
Budget: $50,000
